### Create user
POST http://localhost:8000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "me@example.com",
  "name": "Ilya",
  "provider": "google",
  "provider_sub": "google-oauth2|123456"
}

### List stages
GET http://localhost:8000/stages

### Create job
POST http://localhost:8000/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "company": "Acme",
  "position": "Backend Engineer",
  "source": "LinkedIn",
  "salary": "EUR 4500-5500",
  "stack": "Python, FastAPI, Postgres",
  "notes": "Reached out via recruiter"
}

### List jobs
GET http://localhost:8000/jobs
X-User-Id: 1

### Update job stage (replace 1 with job id, 3 with stage id)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/jobs/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "stage_id": 3
}

### Metrics
GET http://localhost:8000/metrics
X-User-Id: 1
